Application-Level Monitoring Use Cases
API & Integration Health

Monitor success/failure rate of consumed and exposed APIs.

Track timeouts, failed authentications, or schema mismatches.

Slow Screen & API Execution

Monitor average screen load times and long-running queries.

Use APM tools (like New Relic, AppDynamics, or Dynatrace) with OutSystems.

Error & Exception Monitoring

Capture exceptions in Service Center logs.

Alert on high exception rates or specific error patterns.

User Experience Monitoring

Track navigation patterns, session lengths, and device/browser types.

Identify pages/screens with high bounce rates or drop-offs.

Mobile App Crashes

Use crash reporting tools for native or hybrid OutSystems mobile apps (e.g., Firebase Crashlytics).

